"title": "5689: friendlessness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5689: friendlessness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The bitter experience of the absence of friendship, leading to a sense of isolation and despair. It is often blamed on the faithlessness of others or even on God himself.</p>\n<h2>The experience of friendlessness</h2>\n<h3>The darkness of being alone</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:18\">PSA 88:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:8\">PSA 88:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:7\">PSA 102:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:4\">PSA 142:4</a></p>\n<h3>Contempt and rejection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:11-Ps31:12\">PSA 31:11–31:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:11\">PSA 38:11</a></p>\n<h3>Hatred and loathing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:13-Job19:19\">JOB 19:13–19:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:10\">JOB 30:10</a></p>\n<h3>Slander and conspiracy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:13\">PSA 31:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:10\">JER 20:10</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of friendlessness</h2>\n<h3>Elijah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:10\">1KI 19:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:50\">MRK 14:50</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3\">ISA 53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:56\">MAT 26:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:32\">JHN 16:32</a></p>\n<h3>The prodigal son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:16\">LUK 15:16</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The lame man at the pool of Bethesda</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:7\">JHN 5:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Paul</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:16\">2TI 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10-2Tim4:11\">2TI 4:10–4:11</a></p>\n<h2>The undesirability of friendlessness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:18\">GEN 2:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:9-Eccl4:12\">ECC 4:9–4:12</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Cultivating true friends is the way to avoid friendlessness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:1\">1SA 18:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:63\">PSA 119:63</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19\">LUK 16:19</a></p>",
